snippet.title: Void War Trailer
snippet.description: My first "indie" game, circa 2004. Custom 3D engine, playable over the Internet (primarily multiplayer), space combat with Newtonian (ish) physics, ship special abilities,  lots of "terrain" (in the form of gravity wells, asteroids, space stations, debris, etc.)  It was pretty simple, but as an updated "Space War! in 3D" it was fun, especially in multiplayer.
